metadata.description: Jovi's Origins are 5902 Generative artworks using p5.js telling the story of the metahero universe so far. Each artwork contains 9824 stars, 144 of which are black to represent the number of core heroes. 11 'planets' to represent the 9 planet dao's and the 2 moons (regular and the infamous darkside) all of which are randomly generated in size, position, colour and orbiting body.
